<div class="admin-content">
    <hr/>

    <div class="am-g">

        <div class="am-u-sm-12 am-u-md-2 am-u-md-push-10">
            <div class="am-panel am-panel-default">
                <div class="am-panel-hd">实盘账户操作中</div>
                <div class="am-panel-bd">
                    <p>实盘账户登录信息:</p>
                </div>
                {{#if applySummary.checking}}
                    <ul class="am-list am-list-static am-list-border">
                        <li>正在为您分配账户，请稍后再查看</li>
                    </ul>
                {{else}}
                    <ul class="am-list am-list-static am-list-border">
                        <li>交易账户:<strong>{{applySummary.account}}</strong></li>
                        <li>交易密码:<strong>{{applySummary.password}}</strong></li>
                    </ul>
                {{/if}}
                <div class="am-panel-footer">
                {{#unless applySummary.checking}}
                    <p class="am-text-center">股票操盘软件下载</p>
                    <a href="http://www.ihoms.com/www/download/download.do?modelName=2" type="button" class="am-btn am-btn-success am-radius am-center">进入下载页面</a>
                    <p class="am-text-center">下载软件后，用上面账户信息登录即可操作股票</p>
                {{/unless}}
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="am-u-sm-12 am-u-md-10 am-u-md-pull-2">
            <div class="am-panel am-panel-default">
                <div class="am-panel-hd">实盘单号：{{applySummary.serialID}}</div>
                <ul class="am-avg-sm-1 am-avg-md-3 am-margin am-padding am-text-center admin-content-list ">
                    <li><br/>实际操盘金额<br/><span class="am-text-danger am-text-xxl">{{applySummary.amount}}</span></li>
                    <li><br/>缴纳风险保证金<br/><span class="am-text-danger am-text-xxl">{{applySummary.deposit}}</span></li>
                    <li><br/>账户管理费<br/><span class="am-text-danger am-text-xxl">{{applySummary.charge}}</span></li>
                </ul>
                <table class="am-table">
                    <tbody>
                    <tr>
                        <td>亏损预警线:{{applySummary.warnValue}}元</td>
                        <td>亏损平仓线:{{applySummary.sellValue}}</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>开始交易时间:{{applySummary.startDate}}</td>
                        <td>(预计)截止交易日期:{{applySummary.endDate}}</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>投资方向:沪深A股</td>
                        <td>仓位要求:不限制</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>盈利分配:全归您</td>
                        <td></td>
                    </tr>
                    </tbody>
                </table>
            </div>

            {{#unless applySummary.checking}}
            <div id="apply_operation_div" class="am-u-sm-12">
                <ul class="am-avg-sm-1 am-avg-md-5 am-margin am-padding am-text-center admin-content-list">
                    <li><br/><button type="button" class="am-btn am-btn-danger am-radius">我要延期</button><br/><span class="apply-prompt">提示：保证金余额不低于80%时才可以申请延期。</span></li>
                    <li><br/><button id="add-deposit" type="button" class="am-btn am-btn-danger am-radius">追加保证金</button><br/><span class="apply-prompt">提示：保证金余额不足30%时,需要追加保证金至80%。</span></li>
                    <li><br/><button id="get-profit" type="button" class="am-btn am-btn-danger am-radius">提取盈利</button><br/><span class="apply-prompt">提示：您可以将股票中的盈利再提取用于提现或者购买新股票。</span></li>
                    <li><br/><button type="button" class="am-btn am-btn-danger am-radius">加配资金</button><br/><span class="apply-prompt">提示：增加实盘资金需要补足原方案的保证金至80%才可以增加。</span></li>
                    <li><br/><button id="close-apply" type="button" class="am-btn am-btn-danger am-radius">我要结算</button><br/><span class="apply-prompt">提示：如果还要购股票，可以不用结算，继续使用HOMS。</span></li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            {{/unless}}
        </div>
    </div>
    <hr>
</div>

<form name="applyDetailForm">
    <input type="hidden" name="apply_serial_id" id="apply_serial_id" value="{{applySummary.serialID}}">
</form>

<div class="am-modal am-modal-prompt" tabindex="-1" id="close-apply-prompt">
    <div class="am-modal-dialog">
        <div class="am-modal-hd">配资结算</div>
        <div class="am-modal-bd">
            结算前必须先卖出该操盘账户中所有股票，结算后该操盘账户将不能再交易。
        </div>
        <div class="am-modal-footer">
            <span class="am-modal-btn" data-am-modal-cancel>取消</span>
            <span class="am-modal-btn" data-am-modal-confirm>提交</span>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
